.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: trance, rock, r&b, classical, dubstep
5 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, bridge, go, backgammon
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, skateboarding, volleyball, parkour, weightlifting
The people use 5 different means of transport: van, jet-ski, car, quad-bike, bus
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy, daffodil, orchid, daisy

1. the person playing scrabble is the fan of trance
2. the person playing canasta is the person who growsmarigold
3. the person driving the van is the fan of rock
4. the person playing bridge is the person driving the jet-ski
5. the fan of rock is to the right of the fan of r&b
6. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who growsdaisy
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the fan of classical
8. the person driving the car is in the middle
9. the person playing go is on the far left
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is to the left or right of the person who growsorchid
12. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the quad-bike
13. the person playing backgammon is the person who's sport is weightlifting
14. the person playing go is to the left or right of the fan of dubstep

